'''夏緬·潔甘'''（'''Charmaine Dragun'''，{{bd|1978年|3月21日|2007年|11月2日|catIdx=Dragun, Charmaine}}）<ref name=marry>{{cite news | last = Wilson | first = Lauren | title = Newsreader planned to marry | work = The Australian | date = 2007-11-05 | url = http://www.news.com.au/story/0,23599,22701896-2,00.html | accessdate = 2007-11-05 | archive-date = 2007-11-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071105210042/http://www.news.com.au/story/0,23599,22701896-2,00.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>曾是[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]][[十號電視網|第十頻道]]的新聞主播，她生前主持過該頻道於[[珀斯|珀斯]]的五點鐘地區新聞節目。

==出生==
夏緬1978年生于[[西澳大利亞州|西澳]]首府[[珀斯|伯斯]]。

==廣播事業==
夏緬以優異成績畢業于[[伊迪斯科文大學|伊迪斯科文大學]]（Edith Cowan University）之附屬[[西澳表演藝術學院|西澳表演藝術學院]]（Western Australian Academy of Performing Arts；WAAPA），隨後在珀斯的6PR和96FM電臺擔任記者<ref>{{cite news | last = Yeap | first = Sue | title = Home from home for newsreader | work = The West Australian | date = 2005-09-26 }}</ref>；工作表現十分出色，曾經被提名為澳洲的「年度最佳年輕記者」。

她於2002年加盟第十頻道，起初主要報導司法新聞，其後分別於2003年和2004年的夏季擔任後備主播。從2005年7月起主持西澳的五點鐘地區新聞節目<ref>{{cite web | title = Graduate Testimonials from successful graduates | publisher = Edith Cowan University | url = http://www.reachyourpotential.com.au/testimonials.htm | accessdate = 2007-11-03 | archive-date = 2007-11-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071105071207/http://www.reachyourpotential.com.au/testimonials.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。由於第十頻道的地區新聞是從位於[[悉尼|悉尼]]的新聞中心製作的，因此於這段時期她定居於悉尼。

夏緬十分積極參與公益事業，曾大力為西澳的乳癌症患者募捐<ref>{{cite news | last = Bauwens | first = Di | title = Pink Power | work = The West Australian | date = 2007-09-26 }}</ref>。此外，她也十分關心祖國[[克羅地亞|克羅地亞]]；曾于2007年7月返鄉觀光歷史景點並以第一人稱撰寫文章、於7月22日發表在《[[悉尼晨鋒報|悉尼晨鋒報]]》（Sydney Morning Herald）上<ref>{{cite web | title = Charmaine Dragun discovers her heritage in Croatia | work = The Sunday Times | url = http://www.news.com.au/perthnow/story/0,21598,22695978-2761,00.html | accessdate = 2007-11-05 | archive-date = 2012-09-10 | archive-url = https://archive.is/20120910152226/http://www.perthnow.com.au/news/western-australia/draguns-quest-for-croat-roots/story-e6frg13u-1111114793080 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==自殺==
2007年11月2日（悉尼時間）下午4時左右，夏緬縱身跳下位于東悉尼著名的[[断魂谷_(新南威尔士州)|斷魂谷]]（The Gap），因[[憂鬱症|憂鬱症]]自我結束生命，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.postchronicle.com/news/original/article_212113174.shtml|title=Australian News Anchor Suicide: Charmaine Dragun, 29, Jumps To Death|accessdate=2007-11-04|date=2007-11-04|publisher=The Post-Chronicle|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071107055615/http://www.postchronicle.com/news/original/article_212113174.shtml|archive-date=2007-11-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Box | first = Dan | title = Newsreader found dead | work = The Australian | date = 2007-11-03 | url = http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0,25197,22694565-601,00.html | accessdate = 2007-11-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071103141522/http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0,25197,22694565-601,00.html | archive-date = 2007-11-03 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Channel Ten newsreader Charmaine Dragun found dead |work=The Sunday Times |url=http://www.news.com.au/perthnow/story/0,21598,22693062-2761,00.html |accessdate=2007-11-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090515144127/http://www.news.com.au/perthnow/story/0%2C21598%2C22693062-2761%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-05-15 }}</ref>得年29歲。

第十頻道台長{{le|Grant Blackley}}在敘述此事時說：「夏緬是個智慧超群、充滿活力和關心他人的人，同事們無不愛慕著她，我們謹對她的伴侶Simon和家庭表示最衷心的同情和哀悼。」（原文：Charmaine was a highly intelligent, vibrant and caring person, universally liked and admired by her colleagues. Our deepest sympathies go to her partner, Simon, and her family.）<ref>{{cite press release | title = Media Statement from Network Ten | publisher = Network Ten | date = 2007-11-02 | url = http://www.ebroadcast.com.au/enews/charmaine-dragun-021107.html | accessdate = 2007-11-03 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071104093853/http://www.ebroadcast.com.au/enews/charmaine-dragun-021107.html | archivedate = 2007-11-04 }}</ref>

